data.description: This beautiful cabin in the woods is only 55 miles from the Denver International Airport.  Beautiful and well built, the passive solar design is efficient and the in-floor, radiant heat reduces energy costs and provides a cozy feel.  Custom woodwork, majestic vaulted ceilings, picture window views and the peaceful covered patio are all nestled on 5.47 acres in the Pines where wildlife abound for your viewing pleasure.  The detached garage makes a great workshop plus there is an additional she shed/bunk house.  Brand New Stainless Steel appliances, New well pump, New septic tank.  Come see all this property has to offer.
